## 10. Forbidden Patterns

### Nonstop cinematic pacing
- ❌ Every scene at TIER 03+. No silence anywhere.
- ❌ Continuous reveals throughout the page (no "off" frames).
- ❌ Atmosphere intensity at peak throughout.

### Permanent motion density
- ❌ Three or more consecutive TIER 04+ scenes.
- ❌ Two pinned chapters back-to-back.
- ❌ Two chapters with the same density curve adjacent.

### Emotional overdesign
- ❌ Every scene declared "climactic".
- ❌ `type.epic` more than twice per page.
- ❌ Light leak peak in every chapter.
- ❌ WebGL ambient continuously active across all chapters of a page.

### "Everything feels epic"
- ❌ All scenes scored at the same emotional register.
- ❌ Display type in every viewport.
- ❌ Full-bleed image in every viewport.
- ❌ Cursor in its expanded state for > 30% of scroll travel.

### Constant dramatic intensity
- ❌ Music / sound playing throughout (per `sound-behavior-system.mdc`).
- ❌ Slow scroll forced via Lenis tuning beyond `1.4` (already capped).
- ❌ Pinned sections > 2 per page.
- ❌ Vignette intensity peak in every scene.

